name: ComicBookHero - Eskimo Words for Snow
description:
#### ComicBookHero ####

ComicBookHero will be providing their EP for £2! This is the cheapest the product will be and is currently retailing for £3.95 on Apple iTunes.

Get yours before they're sold out. This price is for a limited time only as a start to the tour!

name: The Manchester Festival
description:
On Sunday 27th June, Melomania Records will be hosting their first ever festival at Satans Hollow, Manchester. Doors will open at 3pm, with first band performing at 3.15pm. The line up is:

Eighth Wave
Tall Trees & I, Said the Spy
They Sink Ships, ComicBookHero and Above the Underground
A48 & Call it a day
Last Regards & First of the thieves

Advance prices are: £5
(Vaild for whole day)

Minimum age: 16

Under 21's may be requested for I.D when purchasing Alcohol.
